remarks.summary: Advance notice: Rail strike on Friday, 21 April
remarks.text: Due to a strike by the EVG trade union, there will be considerable restrictions. Almost all train journeys of RE, RB and S-Bahn trains as well as long-distance trains will be cancelled. Subways, trams, buses and ferries will run. More details at www.vbb.de/streik.
